        <instrument_desc>
 
      Instrument Overview
      ===================
      This InSb photometer predates the NSFCAM CCD photometer
      installed at the IRTF in 1993. The only description of
      this instrument known as of this writing is from Rivkin,
      et al. (1995) [RIVKINETAL1995], and is quoted here in its
      entirety:
 
        An InSb photometer with broadband J, H, and K filters
        and two narrowband filters at 2.95 and 3.35 micrometers
        at the Infrared Telescope Facility (IRTF).

        </instrument_desc>
